                        <div data-type="example" id="fs-idm168909584">
                          <h3 class="os-title">
                            <span class="os-title-label">Example</span>
                            <span class="os-number">16.3</span>
                            <span class="os-divider"></span>
                          </h3>
                          <p id="fs-idm148208960">
                            <span
                              data-type="title"
                            >Writing Galvanic Cell Schematics</span>
                            A galvanic cell is fabricated by connecting two half-cells with a salt bridge, one in which a chromium wire is immersed in a 1 M CrCl
                            <sub>3</sub> solution and another in which a copper wire is immersed in 1 M CuCl
                            <sub>2</sub>. Assuming the chromium wire functions as an anode, write the schematic for this cell along with equations for the anode half-reaction, the cathode half-reaction, and the overall cell reaction.
                          </p>
                          <p id="fs-idp124889088">
                            <span data-type="title">Solution</span>
                            Since the chromium wire is stipulated to be the anode, the schematic begins with it and proceeds left-to-right, symbolizing the other cell components until ending with the copper wire cathode:
                          </p>
                          <div data-type="equation" id="fs-idm184234832">
                            <math display="block">
                              <semantics>
                                <mrow>
                                  <mrow>
                                    <mtext>Cr</mtext>
                                    <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>
                                    <mi>s</mi>
                                    <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>
                                    <mo>│</mo>
                                    <mn>1</mn>
                                    <mspace width="0.2em"/>
                                    <mi>M</mi>
                                    <mspace width="0.2em"/>
                                    <msub>
                                      <mrow>
                                        <mtext>CrCl</mtext>
                                      </mrow>
                                      <mn>3</mn>
                                    </msub>
                                    <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>
                                    <mi>a</mi>
                                    <mi>q</mi>
                                    <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>
                                    <mo>║</mo>
                                    <mn>1</mn>
                                    <mspace width="0.2em"/>
                                    <mi>M</mi>
                                    <mspace width="0.2em"/>
                                    <msub>
                                      <mrow>
                                        <mtext>CuCl</mtext>
                                      </mrow>
                                      <mn>2</mn>
                                    </msub>
                                    <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>
                                    <mi>a</mi>
                                    <mi>q</mi>
                                    <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>
                                    <mo>│</mo>
                                    <mtext>Cu</mtext>
                                    <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>
                                    <mi>s</mi>
                                    <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>
                                  </mrow>
                                </mrow>
                                <annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content">
                                  <mrow>
                                    <mtext>Cr</mtext>
                                    <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>
                                    <mi>s</mi>
                                    <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>
                                    <mo>│</mo>
                                    <mn>1</mn>
                                    <mspace width="0.2em"/>
                                    <mi>M</mi>
                                    <mspace width="0.2em"/>
                                    <msub>
                                      <mrow>
                                        <mtext>CrCl</mtext>
                                      </mrow>
                                      <mn>3</mn>
                                    </msub>
                                    <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>
